    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Looking for a reliable ride that still has tons of personality? I\u2019m selling my car and it\u2019s in really solid, dependable shape. It\u2019s been such a joy to drive and has been well-cared for over the years. Whether you're heading to work or hitting the road for a trip, this beauty is ready to go! It runs great and looks even better in person. I\u2019d love for it to go to a good home\u2014come swing by and check it out!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
