      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically robust 2004 BMW M3 (E46) finished in Silver Grey Metallic. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS high-pressure stepless variable valve timing to deliver a linear power band up to an 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and an M-Variable limited-slip differential, ensuring tactile engagement and superior corner-exit traction. Significant preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rear subframe reinforcement and a recent VANOS system overhaul. The chassis remains taut with upgraded polyurethane bushings and refreshed dampers. While the aesthetic reflects honest road use, the performance envelope remains sharp and faithful to its M-division heritage. A purist-spec driver\u2019s car with sorted mechanicals.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Used vehicle. Good condition. Well-maintained. Clean title. Recent service complete. No mechanical issues.",
      "price": 32000.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
